bdglue2.meta.schema

Class DownstreamTableMetaData

  • java.lang.Object
    • bdglue2.meta.schema.DownstreamTableMetaData

  • public class DownstreamTableMetaData
extends Object
    A reduced subset of TableMetaData information that only contains the data that we care about downstream. This lets us decouple the "big data" code from upstream "meta data", whereever that may be coming from. It will also make it easier for us to test the downstream packages independently, as well as hopefully making BDGlue more generally useful.
